    <text id="A7550T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Evans mentions the responsibilities he is about to assume at a new factory and
                    discusses the possibility of a visit to Sibert in the near future.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1868-02-11">Feb 11th 1868</date>
                        <name type="place">Staunton</name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>My Dear Mollie</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>Home again I rived in good time for Brother was looking for me he ask Magnus when
                    I was coming back he thought I was going to Stay three or four days I would have
                    Stayed if he <orig reg="hadn't">hadnt</orig> of had Business to attend to at
                    Court The next time I come I want to Stay from Saturday <orig reg="until"
                    >untill</orig> Thursday for it will be the <orig reg="only">onley</orig> chance
                    I will have They will open the Factory next month &amp; I will be Keep
                    closely confined. I will have to go<pb n="2"/>and return the Same day. I hope I
                    can get <orig reg="off">of</orig> Saturday week to Stay three or four days at
                    your home I know I would Enjoy <orig reg="myself">my Self</orig> Magnus <orig
                        reg="says">sayes</orig> he is going <orig reg="too">two</orig> we could have
                    a nice time Fishing. Ella wants to go <orig reg="too">two</orig> I want Magnus
                    to take her She Says he will think <orig reg="about">a bout</orig> it. I hope
                    your Pa rived home Safe he found the roads very bad and <unclear>ruf</unclear> I
                    told him <orig reg="before">be four</orig> he Started he would have to get Jim
                        <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> Else he Could not get along I thought of you all the way
                    home And Since I<pb n="3"/>I got home <orig reg="too">two</orig> I love you
                    truly &amp; deeply-- yes Passionately I love you more &amp; more Ever
                    day of my life with all my heart &amp; Soul I love you &amp; you <orig
                        reg="only">onley</orig>.</p>

                <p>Ella &amp; <orig reg="family">famley</orig> are all well tell Ham I Sent a
                    plug of tobacco to him by his Pa.</p>

                <p>give my love to your Ma &amp; Pa Ham the Children</p>

                <p>I Send love to you &amp; a Kiss I love you truly &amp; with all my heart
                    God Bless you Good bye </p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>Yours</salute>
                    <signed>DH Evans</signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
